Currently, importing issues from FogBugz would leave the description of the ticket in JIRA empty, because the "description" in FogBugz is actually the very first "Opened By" comment that the user types in during the ticket creation process. This is saved as a comment in JIRA.

Users should have the ability to choose this first comment as a JIRA issue description during the import.

