When user fills out summary line in New Bug screen, do a search of current issues to find similar bugs. Then present the results as possible dupes of the bug they are trying to enter.

Like this: http://screencast.com/t/1egsuO2JHrD

Searching for similar bugs is something everyone should do BEFORE entering a new issue but most people don't do it 100% of the time. This feature would guarantee it is done and would likely result in a reduction in dupes which saves time and money.

