JIRA should include workflow transition validators for standard and custom fields.

Ex: I have a custom field that lets the user select the test status (None, Not planned, Planned, Passed, Failed). I only want to let the user resolve the issue if the field is Not planned or Passed. That way I can make sure that the test was performed.

I know that the plugin "JIRA Suite Utilities" offers some of this, but it also adds other stuff like custom fields and a new tab in the issues view that I am not interested in. Anyway this functionality is important enough to warrant inclusion in the core product.

